text: Stadsparksvallen is a sports ground in the town of Jönköping in Sweden. Opened in 1902, it is the home ground for the Jönköpings Södra IF soccer club. == References == ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1902 establishments in Europe Category:Stadiums in Sweden Category:Sport in Jönköping Category:Buildings and structures in Jönköping Category:1900s establishments in Sweden
